dc_title_s: Map of the city of Gary and vicinity
dc_description_s: Lake County - Indiana |Title supplied by cataloger. Produced as a class project in the Indiana University, Geography Department. Land use hand colored in colored pencil. Base map: Gary (Ind.). Dept. of City Engineer. Map of the City of Gary and vicinity. [1950]. Scale approximately 1:29,000. not '1 inch = 1000 feet.' Donald Guiney.
